        <button class="btn primary custom">Custom
      </div>
	  	<div id="bar" class="container" data-intro='This bar graph displays the keywords relevant to the story of the Tsarnaevs. It does not come as a surprise that &quot;Boston&quot; was the most popular word for this theme. If you hover over a keyword, the scatterplot to the right will update to highlight the articles that contain that keyword.' data-step='3' data-position='top'>
	  	</div>
	  	<div id="scatter" class="container" data-intro='This scatter plot displays all of the articles that relate to the theme as they occur over time in terms of their number of upvotes. For the Boston story, you can see that the most popular article was one of the initial articles reporting the bombings, which spread like wildfire when the story was first released. You can select a range of articles with your mouse to update the bar graph so that it displays only those keywords in the selected articles.' data-step='4' data-position='top'>
	  	</div>
